{
  "texts": [
    "AI focuses on creating systems that perform tasks that usually require human intelligence traits, such as perception, reasoning, learning, and decision-making.",
    "In the context of HCAI, AI provides the technical foundation of systems and ways to build intelligent machines and evaluate their performance for the tasks at hand.A discipline related to AI that is fundamental to HCAI is Machine Learning (ML).",
    "It involves the development of algorithms that enable computers to learn from data and make predictions or decisions based on it [116].",
    "Most recent AI models are based on neural networks, which are a specific type of ML models that have proven to be very versatile and powerful and are the main players in deep learning, a subset of ML focusing on complex neural networks.",
    "Differently from ML, AI also includes expert rule-based systems, firstorder logic systems, symbolic reasoning systems, etc."
  ]
}